title: AP FACT CHECK: Dubious claims about Benghazi, Clinton email
text: Photo: Jacquelyn Martin, AP Democratic presidential candidate and former Secretary of State Hillary Rodham Clinton, looks down during questioning on Capitol Hill in Washington, Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015, before the House Select Committee on Benghazi. Democratic presidential candidate and former Secretary of State... WASHINGTON (AP) — More than a few facts got mangled as a showdown between Hillary Rodham Clinton and her Republican questioners turned into an 11-hour slog.
